# Paper-to-Code Study Rules

- For each major section, include:
  - goal
  - paper concept/equation
  - symbol table
  - code mapping
  - tensor shape notes
  - one sanity check
- Keep equation IDs stable and referenced consistently.
- Use canonical model paths that match implementation and tests.
- Prefer concise technical explanations tied to concrete tensors.
